* Sun Apr 05 2026 Jürgen B. <dev@karakeep.org> 0.2-1
- Add full-text bookmark search (routes to /bookmarks/search endpoint)
- Fix keyboard dismissed on every search keystroke (search fires on Enter or X only)
- Fix X button not reloading full bookmark list after clearing search
- Add search-based filtering for favourites and archived views
- Add pull-down menu items: "Add link", "Add note", filter toggles
- Add cover page with bookmark count, last title, and quick-add action
- Add "Add bookmark" page for creating new link and text-note bookmarks
- Add bookmark detail page with full metadata display and open-in-browser action
- Add archive / unarchive and favourite toggle to bookmark context menu
- Add delete with remorse action to bookmark context menu
- Add pagination with "Load more" footer button
- Add Sailjail Internet permission for network access
- Fix search endpoint routing (was sending ?q= to list endpoint, now uses correct /search path)
- Fix settings not persisting (save per-field on onEditingFinished)
- Fix binding loop on initialPage (use Component.onCompleted instead of onStatusChanged)
- Add integration test suite for Karakeep API (tst_karakeepapi)

* Fri Apr 04 2026 Developer <dev@karakeep.org> 0.1-1
- Initial release
